! GPIO registers values for Power Down: ! The first column contains the GPIO registers names
! The second column contains the GPIO registers values that should be applied during the power down
!!! You can modify the second column (by a hexadecimal value on 2 digits, or by the string NO_VALUE)!!!!!!!!
!!! If you modify it manually, the data will be loaded at the next embedded software start-up !!!!!!!!
!!! This file can be modified also by the TAT PWS panel, by a "SaveConfig" action on "ActOnAnalogBasebandGPIOs" button!!!!!!!!
